snippet.title: Fighters Anthology - USNF'97 Intro & Vietnam Mission 1: Yankee Station
snippet.description:
Fighters Anthology running on Windows 10 without any tweaks. Only official 1.02 patch installed.

Vietnam Campaign was released originally with US Navy Fighters 97 in 1996 for Windows 95.

Sorry for the crappy quality of the video during mission - I captured the video at 800x600 resolution but youtube downscaled it to 480p (640x480).

Next missions will be @ 640x480 so they should look crispier than this since there should be no scaling at all (1:1 conversion).
